      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARD STYLE LEON (1) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 3 lengths at Ballarat in a handy 22.12 beating Paw Estrella. Has the coveted inside box and goes well at this distance. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Looks to have an edge on most of these. JETSTREAM ICON (6) resumed from a break finishing fifth (22.70) at this track in a Free For All. Has a good record here at this journey. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. SCOTT GREYSCALE (2) could manage only third at this track last time but caught the eye when posting a blistering 25.11 over 450m at this track the start prior. Has the ability and can find winning form again. RIGHTEOUS FURY (8) is worth consideration.",
